  <brief_title>Phase 3 Study With Cadazolid in CDAD (AC061A302)</brief_title>
  <official_title>AC-061A302, A Multi-center, Randomized, Double-blind Study to Compare the Efficacy and Safety of Cadazolid Versus Vancomycin in Subjects With Clostridium Difficile-associated Diarrhea (CDAD).</official_title>
