  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Subjects with CDAD are randomized and then treated with study drug for 10 days. At the end
      of treatment, cure is assessed; subjects are then followed-up to assess any disease
      recurrence.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      An interventional study to investigate the efficacy and safety of cadazolid versus
      vancomycin in subjects with Clostridium difficile-Associated Diarrhea (CDAD).
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
